{"version":3,"kind":"Notebook","sha256":"5afceea601548586beb9ef81be21734dd84c785f5666e4cab49d0c6f92450296","slug":"attribute-completeness","location":"/content/attribute_completeness.ipynb","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"Attributvollständigkeit","content_includes_title":false,"kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3 (ipykernel)","language":"python"},"numbering":{"title":{"offset":1}},"thumbnail":"/oqapi-jupyter-book/build/attributvollständigk-5af49df29f457d88e755845de7082dcc.png","exports":[{"format":"ipynb","filename":"attribute_completeness.ipynb","url":"/oqapi-jupyter-book/build/attribute_completene-45efc5bf3eab447859dafae162a8864d.ipynb"}]},"widgets":{},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","kind":"notebook-content","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1},"end":{"line":1,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Der Attributvollständigkeits-Indikator leitet das Verhältnis von OSM-Elementen ab, die ein oder mehrere Attribute besitzen. Abhängig vom Element kannst du aus einer unterschiedlichen Auswahl an Attributen wählen. Wenn du mehr als ein Attribut in einer Anfrage auswählst, werden die Ergebnisse kombiniert und die Ergebnisgrafik zeigt den Prozentsatz aller Elemente, die alle ausgewählten Attribute besitzen.","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1},"end":{"line":1,"column":1}},"key":"ZkpbYbrhOT"}],"key":"kQbkoX2pMR"},{"type":"div","children":[{"type":"image","url":"/oqapi-jupyter-book/build/attributvollständigk-5af49df29f457d88e755845de7082dcc.png","width":300,"key":"Iv7KHEDRq3","urlSource":"../abbildungen/attributvollständigkeit.png"}],"key":"FlRliLNh6v"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In diesem Drop-down-Menü kannst du ein oder mehrere Attribute auswählen.","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"Z2IE6UsJSY"}],"key":"KPJniiewFE"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Methodik","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"key":"E9pXLDqQll"}],"identifier":"methodik","label":"Methodik","html_id":"methodik","implicit":true,"key":"SUsfKMJ3tM"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"-> Intrinsischer Ansatz","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"vwY0Oagnw4"}],"key":"bt3dzGz921"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Berechnet den Prozentsatz der Elemente, die ein bestimmtes Attribut enthalten. Wenn das untersuchte Element eine Liniengeometrie ist, wird die Quote basierend auf der Länge in km berechnet. Für Geometrien vom Typ node wird die Gesamtanzahl aller Elemente mit der Anzahl der Elemente verglichen, die die ausgewählten Attribute aufweisen.","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"NfnEcTr776"}],"key":"NGPdkYrbAR"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ergebnisgrafik","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"rbwd8q5MVJ"}],"identifier":"ergebnisgrafik","label":"Ergebnisgrafik","html_id":"ergebnisgrafik","implicit":true,"key":"i0voOTSjnZ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Die Ergebnisse der Abfrage findest du im Ergebnisprotokoll unten.\nDas grüne, gelbe oder rote Banner oben links zeigt den Attribut-Vollständigkeitsgrad an.","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"OoLxznIXov"}],"key":"HI5X8B78uh"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Es gibt drei Qualitätskategorien:","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"cA6qvBMnUv"}],"key":"jjwPLMUor6"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"niedrige Completeness < 25%","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"z4ldoNZjoc"}],"key":"biIjxXz0Vs"}],"key":"L2olisQC3q"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"mittlere Completeness 25% - 75%","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"Kin7z9HbRF"}],"key":"yQPl7YX7Dk"}],"key":"VJLxbxbfBz"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"hohe Completeness > 75%","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"Fn7t0OBlQX"}],"key":"V1i7tlCXe6"}],"key":"NM9cgKXeOr"}],"key":"aot3saWydh"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Die Schwellenwerte für die Qualitätskategorien wurden durch die Betrachtung der Quotenverteilung vieler Gebiete und Attribute festgelegt und sollten nicht als objektive Metrik verstanden werden.","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"key":"JjHgdblau7"}],"key":"a5V5e49eC9"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Beispiel","position":{"start":{"line":26